{"type":"message","id":"32ed7df4","parentId":"42cc1e2b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:27:57.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"权限有了（calendar:calendar.event:create），但日历创建接口报 400 错误，可能是 API 参数格式问题。\n\n我先记录下来这个任务，你可以手动在飞书里创建这个日程：\n\n**教学中心集中办公**\n- 📅 3月2日（周一）10:00-16:00\n- 📍 教学中心\n- 👥 伟哥、许雯祯、杨哲\n\n我已经查到他们的 open_id 了，等接口问题排查完可以再试。需要我现在看看是什么原因吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":22538,"output":116,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26046,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772357270282}}
