  text/javascript\nsync.js  3.8KB  1544ad0d285907e1b7bb6dbaf5586fa0ba3470c31d595854b36aa97084c56e52  text/javascript\nsync_routine.js  3.1KB  3c12bed332f69367bfe9284ee09a613e5f9c1c6a162c07fc8a106115f212a3e4  text/javascript"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2870,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nfeishu-calendar  feishu-calendar\nSummary: Manage Feishu (Lark) calendars by listing, searching, checking schedules, syncing events, and marking tasks with automated date extraction.\nOwner: autogame-17\nCreated: 2026-02-14T05:21:17.564Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-01T04:02:50.804Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-02-14T05:21:17.564Z\nChangelog: Re-publish after account restoration\nFiles:\nSKILL.md  1.3KB  c1f8eb8697d96ab14ae2e9e99b2f034925adef72bd3e9d09a831ef86492c632b  text/markdown\n_meta.json  134B  9474630cf46b7c0643de6b7d9646186b9aa2b346535e746053b1fb7560e32639  application/json\ncheck.js  3.8KB  2d1460257127af0ceff5e59daa698a197b4c4e58ce4c4ea83ab91f3374316a26  text/javascript\ncheck_master.js  998B  af2777670771a48c8cc22e08b9436476d313a73d2148cc4db6df99a4c0fb5de0  text/javascript\ncleanup.js  3KB  0cef6fe0f647ba2950e94534622366219ac22d71cebb865b1f62e8f87fd7f767  text/javascript\ncreate.js  4.3KB  045adf490631f61836054a890583a5a0187e15cc259068f2951f20b760b5ac64  text/javascript\nlib/CalendarManager.js  3.5KB  631ca297581b9317aacdd12f14dcc10b3a5cd8573402ed8485fd85c384d86c6f  text/javascript\nlist_test.js  645B  f661acd2702b11bd688d17746df0d6ac5254d50aa9d61b7457f21cd8d7300689  text/javascript\npackage-lock.json  21KB  5f8d09832009052c2cd4b4797d8a4b74c1ac22aec8ec05632049ea0118eaf515  application/json\npackage.json  297B  4cae864ae1eb3bcaaab9741a025bc735183fcc8291ea430c5e552faf9f97fcc8  application/json\nsearch_cal.js  936B  9b9dae1f0fedcb6d1fb5a5c3dbc05d7bb0628e0d480791c456e174bddc4e68ce  text/javascript\nsetup_routine.js  5.3KB  cc87a541f1da3197d9f3af4ac7cd0671f462a962e1c735f7aa3df2ec20b5b0af  text/javascript\nsetup_shared.js  3.5KB  0c394b9cb705e1bfa3a2efdfda53c119b515a9ce36092f318850d4666c89dece  text/javascript\nsync.js  3.8KB  1544ad0d285907e1b7bb6dbaf5586fa0ba3470c31d595854b36aa97084c56e52  text/javascript\nsync_routine.js  3.1KB  3c12bed332f69367bfe9284ee09a613e5f9c1c6a162c07fc8a106115f212a3e4  text/javascript","cwd":"/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772357641586}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbe1a6e8","parentId":"8ba8426c","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:34:06.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个技能有 create.js，应该能创建日程。让我先看看 SKILL.md 内容，确认安全后再安装："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_05d1701a0c6b4ea6997c2e80","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect feishu-calendar --file SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1083,"output":46,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30825,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772357641589}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1e49576","parentId":"bbe1a6e8","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:34:09.075Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_05d1701a0c6b4ea6997c2e80","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n# feishu-calendar\n\nManage Feishu (Lark) Calendars. Use this skill to list calendars, check schedules, and sync events.\n\n## Usage\n\n### List Calendars\nCheck available calendars and their IDs.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/list_test.js\n```\n\n### Search Calendar\nFind a calendar by name/summary.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/search_cal.js\n```\n\n### Check Master's Calendar\nSpecific check for the Master's calendar status.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/check_master.js\n```\n\n### Sync Routine\nRun the calendar synchronization routine (syncs events to local state/memory).\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/sync_routine.js\n```\n\n## Setup\nRequires `FEISHU_APP_ID` and `FEISHU_APP_SECRET` in `.env`.\n\n## Standard Protocol: Task Marking\n**Trigger**: User says \"Mark this task\" or \"Remind me to...\".\n**Action**:\n1. **Analyze**: Extract date/time (e.g., \"Feb 4th\" -> YYYY-MM-04).\n2. **Execute**: Run `create.js` with `--attendees` set to the requester's ID.\n3. **Format**:\n   ```bash\n   node skills/feishu-calendar/create.js --summary \"Task: <Title>\" --desc \"<Context>\" --start \"<ISO>\" --end \"<ISO+1h>\" --attendees \"<User_ID>\"\n   ```\n\n### Setup Shared Calendar\nCreate a shared calendar for a project and add members.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/setup_shared.js --name \"Project Name\" --desc \"Description\" --members \"ou_1,ou_2\" --role \"writer\"\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2742,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n# feishu-calendar\n\nManage Feishu (Lark) Calendars. Use this skill to list calendars, check schedules, and sync events.\n\n## Usage\n\n### List Calendars\nCheck available calendars and their IDs.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/list_test.js\n```\n\n### Search Calendar\nFind a calendar by name/summary.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/search_cal.js\n```\n\n### Check Master's Calendar\nSpecific check for the Master's calendar status.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/check_master.js\n```\n\n### Sync Routine\nRun the calendar synchronization routine (syncs events to local state/memory).\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/sync_routine.js\n```\n\n## Setup\nRequires `FEISHU_APP_ID` and `FEISHU_APP_SECRET` in `.env`.\n\n## Standard Protocol: Task Marking\n**Trigger**: User says \"Mark this task\" or \"Remind me to...\".\n**Action**:\n1. **Analyze**: Extract date/time (e.g., \"Feb 4th\" -> YYYY-MM-04).\n2. **Execute**: Run `create.js` with `--attendees` set to the requester's ID.\n3. **Format**:\n   ```bash\n   node skills/feishu-calendar/create.js --summary \"Task: <Title>\" --desc \"<Context>\" --start \"<ISO>\" --end \"<ISO+1h>\" --attendees \"<User_ID>\"\n   ```\n\n### Setup Shared Calendar\nCreate a shared calendar for a project and add members.\n```bash\nnode skills/feishu-calendar/setup_shared.js --name \"Project Name\" --desc \"Description\" --members \"ou_1,ou_2\" --role \"writer\"\n```","cwd":"/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772357649072}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d1375e4","parentId":"e1e49576","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:34:13.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c4dbd46ff60644afafa0f493","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect feishu-calendar --file create.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2533,"output":21,"cacheRead":28672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772357649075}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8890904","parentId":"8d1375e4","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:34:16.118Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c4dbd46ff60644afafa0f493","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nconst { program } = require('commander');\nconst Lark = require('@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk');\nrequire('dotenv').config({ path: require('path').resolve(__dirname, '../../.env') });\n\nconst APP_ID = process.env.FEISHU_APP_ID;\nconst APP_SECRET = process.env.FEISHU_APP_SECRET;\n\nif (!APP_ID || !APP_SECRET) {\n    console.error('Error: FEISHU_APP_ID or FEISHU_APP_SECRET not set.');\n    process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst client = new Lark.Client({\n    appId: APP_ID,\n    appSecret: APP_SECRET,\n});\n\nprogram\n    .requiredOption('--summary <text>', 'Event title')\n    .requiredOption('--start <time>', 'Start time (YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm)')\n    .requiredOption('--end <time>', 'End time (YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm)')\n    .option('--desc <text>', 'Description')\n    .option('--calendar <id>', 'Target Calendar ID')\n    .option('--attendees <ids>', 'Comma-separated user OpenIDs to invite')\n    .parse(process.argv);\n\nconst options = program.opts();\n\nasync function createEvent() {\n    try {\n        const startTs = Math.floor(new Date(options.start).getTime() / 1000);\n        const endTs = Math.floor(new Date(options.end).getTime() / 1000);\n\n        if (isNaN(startTs) || isNaN(endTs)) {\n            console.error('Invalid date format.');\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        // Auto-discover calendar if not provided\n        let targetCalendarId = options.calendar;\n        if (!targetCalendarId) {\n             try {\n                 const calList = await client.calendar.calendar.list();\n                 if (calList.code === 0 && calList.data.calendar_list && calList.data.calendar_list.length > 0) {\n                     // Prefer 'OpenClaw Assistant', then 'primary', then first in list\n                     const botCal = calList.data.calendar_list.find(c => c.summary === 'OpenClaw Assistant') || calList.data.calendar_list[0];\n                     targetCalendarId = botCal.calendar_id;\n                     console.log(`Auto-selected calendar: ${botCal.summary} (${targetCalendarId})`);\n                 }\n             } catch (e) {\n                 console.warn(\"Failed to auto-discover calendar:\", e.message);\n             }\n        }\n\n        if (!targetCalendarId) {\n            console.error(\"No calendar found. Please create one first.\");\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        const attendees = [];\n        if (options.attendees) {\n            options.attendees.split(',').forEach(id => {\n                attendees.push({\n                    type: 'user',\n                    user_id: id.trim()\n                });\n            });\n        }\n\n        console.log(`Creating event on calendar: ${targetCalendarId}`);\n\n        // Direct Request with Fallback\n        \n        async function tryCreate(calId) {\n            return await client.request({\n                method: 'POST',\n                url: `/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars/${encodeURIComponent(calId)}/events?user_id_type=open_id`,\n                data: {\n                    summary: options.summary,\n                    description: options.desc || '',\n                    need_notification: true, // Explicitly request notification\n                    start_time: { timestamp: String(startTs), timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai' },\n                    end_time: { timestamp: String(endTs), timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai' },\n                    attendees: attendees.length > 0 ? attendees : undefined,\n                    vchat: { vc_type: 'no_meeting' }\n                }\n            });\n        }\n\n        let response = await tryCreate(targetCalendarId);\n\n        // Fallback to primary if specific ID fails (permission issue)\n        if (response.code !== 0 && targetCalendarId !== 'primary') {\n             console.log(`Creation failed on ${targetCalendarId} (${response.code}). Retrying on 'primary'...`);\n             response = await tryCreate('primary');\n        }\n\n        if (response.code !== 0) {\n            console.error(`Feishu API Error: ${response.msg} (Code: ${response.code})`);\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        const evt = response.data.event;\n        console.log(`✅ Event Created: ${evt.summary}`);\n        console.log(`   Time: ${new Date(parseInt(evt.start_time.timestamp)*1000).toLocaleString()}`);\n        console.log(`   Link: ${evt.app_link}`);\n\n    } catch (e) {\n        console.error('Error:', e.message);\n        if (e.response) console.error('Data:', JSON.stringify(e.response.data));\n    }\n}\n\ncreateEvent();"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3108,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nconst { program } = require('commander');\nconst Lark = require('@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk');\nrequire('dotenv').config({ path: require('path').resolve(__dirname, '../../.env') });\n\nconst APP_ID = process.env.FEISHU_APP_ID;\nconst APP_SECRET = process.env.FEISHU_APP_SECRET;\n\nif (!APP_ID || !APP_SECRET) {\n    console.error('Error: FEISHU_APP_ID or FEISHU_APP_SECRET not set.');\n    process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst client = new Lark.Client({\n    appId: APP_ID,\n    appSecret: APP_SECRET,\n});\n\nprogram\n    .requiredOption('--summary <text>', 'Event title')\n    .requiredOption('--start <time>', 'Start time (YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm)')\n    .requiredOption('--end <time>', 'End time (YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm)')\n    .option('--desc <text>', 'Description')\n    .option('--calendar <id>', 'Target Calendar ID')\n    .option('--attendees <ids>', 'Comma-separated user OpenIDs to invite')\n    .parse(process.argv);\n\nconst options = program.opts();\n\nasync function createEvent() {\n    try {\n        const startTs = Math.floor(new Date(options.start).getTime() / 1000);\n        const endTs = Math.floor(new Date(options.end).getTime() / 1000);\n\n        if (isNaN(startTs) || isNaN(endTs)) {\n            console.error('Invalid date format.');\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        // Auto-discover calendar if not provided\n        let targetCalendarId = options.calendar;\n        if (!targetCalendarId) {\n             try {\n                 const calList = await client.calendar.calendar.list();\n                 if (calList.code === 0 && calList.data.calendar_list && calList.data.calendar_list.length > 0) {\n                     // Prefer 'OpenClaw Assistant', then 'primary', then first in list\n                     const botCal = calList.data.calendar_list.find(c => c.summary === 'OpenClaw Assistant') || calList.data.calendar_list[0];\n                     targetCalendarId = botCal.calendar_id;\n                     console.log(`Auto-selected calendar: ${botCal.summary} (${targetCalendarId})`);\n                 }\n             } catch (e) {\n                 console.warn(\"Failed to auto-discover calendar:\", e.message);\n             }\n        }\n\n        if (!targetCalendarId) {\n            console.error(\"No calendar found. Please create one first.\");\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        const attendees = [];\n        if (options.attendees) {\n            options.attendees.split(',').forEach(id => {\n                attendees.push({\n                    type: 'user',\n                    user_id: id.trim()\n                });\n            });\n        }\n\n        console.log(`Creating event on calendar: ${targetCalendarId}`);\n\n        // Direct Request with Fallback\n        \n        async function tryCreate(calId) {\n            return await client.request({\n                method: 'POST',\n                url: `/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars/${encodeURIComponent(calId)}/events?user_id_type=open_id`,\n                data: {\n                    summary: options.summary,\n                    description: options.desc || '',\n                    need_notification: true, // Explicitly request notification\n                    start_time: { timestamp: String(startTs), timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai' },\n                    end_time: { timestamp: String(endTs), timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai' },\n                    attendees: attendees.length > 0 ? attendees : undefined,\n                    vchat: { vc_type: 'no_meeting' }\n                }\n            });\n        }\n\n        let response = await tryCreate(targetCalendarId);\n\n        // Fallback to primary if specific ID fails (permission issue)\n        if (response.code !== 0 && targetCalendarId !== 'primary') {\n             console.log(`Creation failed on ${targetCalendarId} (${response.code}). Retrying on 'primary'...`);\n             response = await tryCreate('primary');\n        }\n\n        if (response.code !== 0) {\n            console.error(`Feishu API Error: ${response.msg} (Code: ${response.code})`);\n            process.exit(1);\n        }\n\n        const evt = response.data.event;\n        console.log(`✅ Event Created: ${evt.summary}`);\n        console.log(`   Time: ${new Date(parseInt(evt.start_time.timestamp)*1000).toLocaleString()}`);\n        console.log(`   Link: ${evt.app_link}`);\n\n    } catch (e) {\n        console.error('Error:', e.message);\n        if (e.response) console.error('Data:', JSON.stringify(e.response.data));\n    }\n}\n\ncreateEvent();","cwd":"/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772357656115}}
{"type":"message","id":"3bfdbfc7","parentId":"b8890904","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:34:26.780Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码看起来安全，用的是飞书官方 SDK。问题是它需要 `FEISHU_APP_ID` 和 `FEISHU_APP_SECRET`，这是自建应用的凭证，而当前 OpenClaw 用的是飞书商店应用的 OAuth 授权方式。\n\n让我检查一下当前环境有没有这些配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f4341287df5f4c2b8eb604a6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/.env 2>/dev/null || echo \"No .env found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2613,"output":94,"cacheRead":29568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772357656118}}
