status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1890,"aggregated":"[info]: [ 'client ready' ]\n=== Listing calendars ===\nCode: 0\n  - feishu.cn_7xnp3Pb3MOULuPnBlgglEe@group.calendar.feishu.cn 教学中心集中办公 primary: undefined\n  - feishu.cn_ZTXplj9yKRLcmDRuJCnO0c@group.calendar.feishu.cn 教学中心集中办公 primary: undefined\n  - feishu.cn_Ci9T1kqXRtbwS3RWmTRbGe@group.calendar.feishu.cn OpenClaw primary: undefined\n  - feishu.cn_XPhMNlWBS0qz08CnYIrb0g@group.calendar.feishu.cn 刘伟(openclaw) primary: undefined\n\n=== Creating event on calendar: feishu.cn_7xnp3Pb3MOULuPnBlgglEe@group.calendar.feishu.cn ===\nCreate response: {\n  \"code\": 0,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"event\": {\n      \"app_link\": \"https://applink.feishu.cn/client/calendar/event/detail?calendarId=7612098791101074628&key=0eecd809-363b-4f25-94ba-9970daa4e867&originalTime=0&startTime=1772416800\",\n      \"attendee_ability\": \"none\",\n      \"color\": -1,\n      \"create_time\": \"1772357839\",\n      \"description\": \"地点: 教学中心\\\\n参与人: 伟哥、许雯祯、杨哲\",\n      \"end_time\": {\n        \"timestamp\": \"1772438400\",\n        \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"event_id\": \"0eecd809-363b-4f25-94ba-9970daa4e867_0\",\n      \"free_busy_status\": \"busy\",\n      \"is_exception\": false,\n      \"location\": {\n        \"address\": \"\",\n        \"latitude\": 0,\n        \"longitude\": 0,\n        \"name\": \"教学中心\"\n      },\n      \"organizer_calendar_id\": \"feishu.cn_7xnp3Pb3MOULuPnBlgglEe@group.calendar.feishu.cn\",\n      \"recurrence\": \"\",\n      \"self_rsvp_status\": \"accept\",\n      \"start_time\": {\n        \"timestamp\": \"1772416800\",\n        \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"status\": \"confirmed\",\n      \"summary\": \"教学中心集中办公\",\n      \"visibility\": \"default\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"msg\": \"success\"\n}","cwd":"/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772357839758}}
