{"type":"message","id":"c1aef7dd","parentId":"d9539e10","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:51:55.640Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_85cdcd6d9411484abb7b8cbb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"mem0ai/mem0 - 48325 stars - Universal memory layer for AI Agents\nMemTensor/HaluMem - 111 stars - HaluMem is the first operation level hallucination evaluation benchmark tailored to agent memory systems.\npinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp - 87 stars - ✨ mem0 MCP Server: A memory system using mem0 for AI applications with model context protocl (MCP) integration. Enables long-term memory for AI agents as a drop-in MCP server.\nAIAnytime/Agent-Memory-Playground - 32 stars - Agent Memory Playground: AI Agent Memory Design & Optimization Techniques\nRBKunnela/ALMA-memory - 17 stars - Persistent memory for AI agents - Learn, remember, improve.   Alternative to Mem0 with scoped learning, anti-patterns,   multi-agent sharing, and MCP integration.\nryaker/mcp-mem0-general - 16 stars - OpenAI just added memory across your chats across your openAI account. But wouldn't it be awesome to have general AI memory across all your interactions with any and all AI tools, IDEs, chatbots.... Now if it supports MCP you can with https://mem0.ai/ Give Claude desktop memory. Give cursor or windsurf memory across sessions or different projects.\nextrawest/fastapi-langgraph-chatbot-with-vector-store-memory-mcp-tools-and-voice-mode - 11 stars - A scalable AI chatbot platform built with FastAPI and LangGraph, featuring multi-agent orchestration, multi-tenant vector storage, cross-chat memory, and voice call capabilities through LiveKit integration.\nbiojazzard/mcp-mem0-docker - 7 stars - MCP-Mem0-docker: Long-Term Memory for AI Agents based on mem0.ai\nyashksaini-coder/mastra-mem0-backend - 6 stars - Docker deployed mastra AI agent server, with tools, memory and workflow \n0sparsh2/memorable-ai - 6 stars - Memorable-AI remembers everything automatically— Jut 2 lines of code. Uses research-backed techniques from Mem0 + interceptor architecture from Memori + optional graph from Supermemory."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2030,"aggregated":"mem0ai/mem0 - 48325 stars - Universal memory layer for AI Agents\nMemTensor/HaluMem - 111 stars - HaluMem is the first operation level hallucination evaluation benchmark tailored to agent memory systems.\npinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp - 87 stars - ✨ mem0 MCP Server: A memory system using mem0 for AI applications with model context protocl (MCP) integration. Enables long-term memory for AI agents as a drop-in MCP server.\nAIAnytime/Agent-Memory-Playground - 32 stars - Agent Memory Playground: AI Agent Memory Design & Optimization Techniques\nRBKunnela/ALMA-memory - 17 stars - Persistent memory for AI agents - Learn, remember, improve.   Alternative to Mem0 with scoped learning, anti-patterns,   multi-agent sharing, and MCP integration.\nryaker/mcp-mem0-general - 16 stars - OpenAI just added memory across your chats across your openAI account. But wouldn't it be awesome to have general AI memory across all your interactions with any and all AI tools, IDEs, chatbots.... Now if it supports MCP you can with https://mem0.ai/ Give Claude desktop memory. Give cursor or windsurf memory across sessions or different projects.\nextrawest/fastapi-langgraph-chatbot-with-vector-store-memory-mcp-tools-and-voice-mode - 11 stars - A scalable AI chatbot platform built with FastAPI and LangGraph, featuring multi-agent orchestration, multi-tenant vector storage, cross-chat memory, and voice call capabilities through LiveKit integration.\nbiojazzard/mcp-mem0-docker - 7 stars - MCP-Mem0-docker: Long-Term Memory for AI Agents based on mem0.ai\nyashksaini-coder/mastra-mem0-backend - 6 stars - Docker deployed mastra AI agent server, with tools, memory and workflow \n0sparsh2/memorable-ai - 6 stars - Memorable-AI remembers everything automatically— Jut 2 lines of code. Uses research-backed techniques from Mem0 + inter