{"type":"message","id":"d2188228","parentId":"59b9b1b0","timestamp":"2026-03-01T11:20:02.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**✅ 内容创作 Agent 创建完成！**\n\n## 小笔杆 ✍️\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **ID** | content-writer |\n| **名字** | 小笔杆 |\n| **专长** | 公众号写作、五句话介绍、课程主持词、内部学习资料 |\n| **工作目录** | `/Users/liuwei/SynologyDrive/0050Project/GW.Content` |\n| **模型** | Claude Opus 4.5（写作更强） |\n\n## 如何使用\n\n**方式1：让我 spawn 子 agent**\n```\n帮我用小笔杆写一篇关于XX的公众号文章\n```\n\n**方式2：直接调用**\n```bash\nopenclaw agent --agent content-writer --message \"写一篇关于流程型组织的公众号文章\"\n```\n\n要测试一下吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":8874,"output":183,"cacheRead":63744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772363991632}}
