{"type":"message","id":"fe7658b7","parentId":"818f6c8d","timestamp":"2026-03-01T11:34:55.315Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a1b1bdfeb8914f0f9f00670e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-01 (周日)\n\n## 今日事项\n- 14:46 新会话启动\n- 14:53 伟哥问我核心任务 → 发现 memory 文件还没建\n- 14:54 开始初始化 memory 系统\n- 17:32 帮伟哥创建日程「教学中心集中办公」3/2 10:00-16:00，地点教学中心，参与人：伟哥、许雯祯、杨哲\n- 17:42 伟哥发来 ClawIntelligentMemory 方案，研究 AI 记忆系统\n- 17:48 搜索 GitHub 找到多个记忆方案：Mem0(48k stars, YC投资)、MemOS(6k)、OpenViking(4k)、MemoryOS(1.2k)\n- 17:54 伟哥选择 Mem0，找到 openclaw-mem0 插件并安装成功\n- 17:57 Gateway 重启中（安装插件后需要重启）\n\n## 备注\n- 今天是小龙虾正式「醒来」的日子，memory 系统从零开始建\n- Mem0 插件已安装，支持本地 Qwen3 嵌入模型，声称节省 70-90% token\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772364895310}}
{"type":"message","id":"f93927a6","parentId":"fe7658b7","timestamp":"2026-03-01T11:35:14.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当前时间 19:33，检查一下明天（周一）的日程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c661e01d73a848428aec94bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/openclaw/extensions/feishu && node -e '\nconst Lark = require(\"@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk\");\n\nconst client = new Lark.Client({\n  appId: \"cli_a913c55ee839dcd2\",\n  appSecret: \"oO0CB8flBudXU5SEz2zBOe8GLiY4gdOo\",\n});\n\nasync function checkCalendar() {\n  const myCal = \"feishu.cn_XPhMNlWBS0qz08CnYIrb0g@group.calendar.feishu.cn\";\n  \n  // 明天的时间范围\n  const tomorrowStart = new Date(\"2026-03-02T00:00:00+08:00\");\n  const tomorrowEnd = new Date(\"2026-03-02T23:59:59+08:00\");\n  \n  const startTs = Math.floor(tomorrowStart.getTime() / 1000);\n  const endTs = Math.floor(tomorrowEnd.getTime() / 1000);\n  \n  console.log(\"检查 3月2日（周一）的日程...\");\n  \n  const resp = await client.calendar.calendarEvent.search({\n    data: {\n      query: \"\",\n      filter: {\n        start_time: startTs,\n        end_time: endTs,\n        calendar_ids: [myCal]\n      }\n    }\n  });\n  \n  if (resp.code === 0 && resp.data?.events?.length > 0) {\n    console.log(\"找到\", resp.data.events.length, \"个日程:\");\n    resp.data.events.forEach(e => {\n      const evt = e.event || e;\n      const start = new Date(parseInt(evt.start_time?.timestamp) * 1000).toLocaleString(\"zh-CN\", {timeZone: \"Asia/Shanghai\"});\n      console.log(\"  -\", evt.summary, \"@\", start);\n    });\n  } else {\n    console.log(\"没有找到日程\");\n  }\n}\n\ncheckCalendar().catch(e => console.error(\"Error:\", e.message));\n'","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":70362,"output":454,"cacheRead":3008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73824,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772364895315}}
