{"type":"compaction","id":"b40e70af","parentId":"7e5d1bc3","timestamp":"2026-03-01T11:55:50.250Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Create a Feishu calendar event for \"教学中心集中办公\" on March 2nd, 10:00-16:00 at 教学中心 with attendees: 伟哥、许雯祯、杨哲\n2. Research and install a memory system for OpenClaw AI assistant (小龙虾)\n3. User wants the AI to solve problems independently without taking shortcuts\n4. Create a specialized content-writing agent for the GW.Content project\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User (伟哥) prefers the AI to figure things out itself, iterate, search, and troubleshoot rather than asking for shortcuts\n- User works at 高维学堂\n- Colleagues: 军哥(刘军), KK(林传科), 碧容(陈碧容), 雯祯(许雯祯), 大眼(杨哲)\n- User prefers simple explanations over technical jargon (e.g., \"spawn子agent\" was confusing)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created calendar event \"教学中心集中办公\" for March 2, 2026 10:00-16:00 at 教学中心\n- [x] Event created on \"刘伟\" calendar (calendar_id: feishu.cn_XPhMNlWBS0qz08CnYIrb0g@group.calendar.feishu.cn)\n- [x] Added attendees via open_ids (伟哥, 许雯祯, 杨哲)\n- [x] Researched AI memory systems via GitHub API - found: Mem0 (48k stars, YC-backed), MemOS (6k), OpenViking (4k), MemoryOS (1.2k)\n- [x] User chose Mem0\n- [x] Found openclaw-mem0 plugin (github.com/1960697431/openclaw-mem0)\n- [x] Installed openclaw-mem0 plugin successfully via install script\n- [x] Updated memory log for 2026-03-01.md\n- [x] Created content-writing agent \"小笔杆\" (content-writer) with config at ~/.openclaw/agents/content-writer/\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Verify Mem0 plugin is working correctly after Gateway restart\n\n### Blocked\n- (Previous Gateway restart issue appears resolved - agent was created successfully)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Feishu Calendar API Debug**: Native feishu_calendar tool returned 400 errors; worked around by directly calling Lark SDK with correct calendar_id discovery\n- **Memory System Choice**: User selected Mem0 over MemOS/ClawIntelligentMemory based on YC backing and 48k stars popularity\n- **Content Agent Model**: Configured \"小笔杆\" to use Claude Opus 4.5 for better writing quality\n- **Calendar API Response**: Events returned in `items` array (not `events`) - important for future queries\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Verify Mem0 plugin is functioning correctly\n2. Test \"小笔杆\" agent with an actual content creation task when user requests\n\n## Critical Context\n- Feishu App credentials in ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json: appId: cli_a913c55ee839dcd2\n- User open_ids: 伟哥=ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209, 许雯祯=ou_fd220137ca3825fea85c1a7ef411c261, 杨哲=ou_f396ae36f9888e511a65a32128f422ad\n- Created event link: https://applink.feishu.cn/client/calendar/event/detail?calendarId=7609522120728906974&key=b3a0e1c7-0dc6-46d5-a9fe-6091c5535eba&originalTime=0&startTime=1772416800\n- Mem0 plugin installed at: ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-mem0/\n- Memory log: ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md\n- AI persona: \"小龙虾\" (lobster), digital assistant, 7x24 available\n- **Content Agent \"小笔杆\"**:\n  - Config: ~/.openclaw/agents/content-writer/openclaw.json\n  - Workspace: /Users/liuwei/SynologyDrive/0050Project/GW.Content\n  - Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-5\n  - Capabilities: 公众号写作, 五句话介绍, 课程主持词, 内部学习资料整理\n- **HEARTBEAT.md**: Located at ~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md - defines periodic check tasks (email, calendar, memory logs)\n- **Current model in use**: GLM-5 (zai/glm-5) - user's default model\n- **March 2, 2026 10:00-16:00**: \"教学中心集中办公\" at 教学中心 (confirmed via calendar API)\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- Write a WeChat public account article (公众号文章) about how to write the \"O\" (Objective) component in OGSM framework\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Article should be in Chinese (based on user's request language)\n- Topic focus specifically on the \"O\" (Objective) element of OGSM methodology\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Received user request for OGSM \"O\" article\n- [x] Searched for OGSM-related reference materials in the content repository\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Reading reference materials to gather content\n- [ ] Writing the public account article\n\n### Blocked\n- None currently\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Search for existing materials**: Assistant decided to leverage internal course content/knowledge base for OGSM reference materials rather than generating from scratch\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Read the found OGSM-related files to extract relevant content about \"O\" (Objective)\n2. Draft the public account article based on the reference materials\n3. Format appropriately for WeChat public account publication\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Found OGSM reference files** (potential sources for article content):\n  - `/Users/liuwei/SynologyDrive/0050Project/GW.Content/01_课程知识库/ogsm(260110)/` - contains multiple txt files (ogsm01.txt, ogsm03.txt, ogsm04.txt)\n  - `/Users/liuwei/SynologyDrive/0050Project/GW.Content/内部学习资料/2006年会/02_2026_OGSM战略.md`\n  - `/Users/liuwei/SynologyDrive/0050Project/GW.Content/01_课程知识库/ogsm/OGSM业务规划与执行 袁园 9.8 深圳.txt`\n  - Course scripts and introduction materials for OGSM课程 also available\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/agents/content-writer/IDENTITY.md\n/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md\n/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"4746baab","tokensBefore":108679,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/agents/content-writer/IDENTITY.md","/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md","/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"]},"fromHook":true}
