{"type":"message","id":"b8f0f345","parentId":"87a96430","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:04:53.316Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5fc46c7ed41e4cc4831ee137","toolName":"feishu_doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"title\": \"OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了\",\n  \"content\": \"OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了\\n\",\n  \"revision_id\": 1,\n  \"block_count\": 1,\n  \"block_types\": {\n    \"Page\": 1\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"title":"OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了","content":"OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了\n","revision_id":1,"block_count":1,"block_types":{"Page":1}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772366693314}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba259ef7","parentId":"b8f0f345","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:05:00.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"又是只有标题。飞书 API 写入有问题。让我换个方式，先读一下 skill 看看正确用法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2dc72aae08e74f1b88689a0d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/liuwei/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":46087,"output":59,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772366693317}}
{"type":"message","id":"49404c44","parentId":"ba259ef7","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:05:00.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2dc72aae08e74f1b88689a0d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\nAppends markdown to end of document.\n\n### Create Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\" }\n```\n\nWith folder:\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\", \"folder_token\": \"fldcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### List Blocks\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"list_blocks\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns full block data including tables, images. Use this to read structured content.\n\n### Get Single Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Update Block Text\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update_block\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\",\n  \"content\": \"New text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"delete_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n## Reading Workflow\n\n1. Start with `action: \"read\"` - get plain text + statistics\n2. Check `block_types` in response for Table, Image, Code, etc.\n3. If structured content exists, use `action: \"list_blocks\"` for full data\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      doc: true # default: true\n```\n\n**Note:** `feishu_wiki` depends on this tool - wiki page content is read/written via `feishu_doc`.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `docx:document`, `docx:document:readonly`, `docx:document.block:convert`, `drive:drive`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772366700624}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d52d38a","parentId":"49404c44","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:05:24.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看起来用法是对的。让我试试用 append 而不是 create 时直接带 content："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c3765dec2a14a599fa78a0a","name":"feishu_doc","arguments":{"action":"create","title":"OGSM之O怎么写"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":58004,"output":42,"cacheRead":5184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772366700628}}
{"type":"message","id":"a38ba923","parentId":"7d52d38a","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:05:25.117Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3c3765dec2a14a599fa78a0a","toolName":"feishu_doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"document_id\": \"W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd\",\n  \"title\": \"OGSM之O怎么写\",\n  \"url\": \"https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd\"\n}"}],"details":{"document_id":"W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd","title":"OGSM之O怎么写","url":"https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772366725115}}
{"type":"message","id":"984209c9","parentId":"a38ba923","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:06:08.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f9fe96a1c0864d1bae31000f","name":"feishu_doc","arguments":{"action":"write","doc_token":"W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd","content":"# OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了\n\n用 OGSM 做年度规划的公司越来越多。但很多人卡在第一步：O（战略目的）怎么写？写得太空，团队看不懂；写得太细，又变成 KPI。\n\n## 先讲一个故事\n\n1927年，红军上井冈山。当时的战略方向是\"团结群众\"。方向没毛病，但执行效果很差——小战士们经常偷老百姓的红薯和芋头。\n\n问题出在哪？\"团结群众\"这四个字太抽象了。\n\n后来，毛泽东把它改成了七个字：\"不拿老百姓一针一线\"。\n\n意思没变，但执行偏差一下子就没了。这就是 O 的写法精髓：**从抽象到具体，从概念到行动。**\n\n## O 是什么？不是什么？\n\nOGSM 里的 O（Objective），准确来说应该叫战略目的或方向性目标。\n\n- 它回答：我们今年要去哪里？\n- 它不回答：我们要去多少？\n\n举个例子：\n- 错误：O：销售额增长30%（这是 G）\n- 正确：O：攻克华东市场，建立区域标杆\n\nO 是定性的方向，G 是定量的刻度。\n\n## O 怎么写？三个原则\n\n**原则一：一句话能说清**\n\n\"凡是能被执行的战略都是通俗易懂的。\"测试方法：随便抓一个基层员工复述公司的 O，如果他说不出来，说明写得太复杂。\n\n**原则二：具象化描述**\n\n\"团结群众\" vs \"不拿老百姓一针一线\"——后者能直接指导行动。越具象，越不容易有歧义。\n\n**原则三：对齐公司战略**\n\n部门级的 O 是从公司级 O 分解下来的，不是拍脑袋想出来的。\n\n## 三种错误写法\n\n1. 把 O 写成数字——\"营收突破10亿\"是 G 不是 O\n2. 写成正确的废话——\"提升核心竞争力\"说了等于没说\n3. O 写太多——一页纸上 O 最好只有 1-2 个\n\n## 写在最后\n\nO 是最\"虚\"的那个，但恰恰最要写\"实\"。O 写歪了，后面的 G、S、M 全都会歪。\n\n好的 O 就像\"不拿老百姓一针一线\"——简单、具体、每个人都能听懂。\n\n---\n\n*核心观点来自高维学堂《OGSM业务规划与执行》课程，袁园老师主讲。*"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":55373,"output":552,"cacheRead":7936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772366725118}}
