{"type":"message","id":"36f7a5d2","parentId":"a7149523","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:36:01.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d62cd01b45d04bf1bcfadaf9","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"📝 **《OGSM 里 O 怎么写？很多人第一步就错了》**\n\n用 OGSM 做年度规划的公司越来越多，但很多人卡在第一步：O（战略目的）怎么写？\n\n这篇文章从高维学堂《OGSM业务规划与执行》课程中提炼了核心观点，用\"团结群众\"→\"不拿老百姓一针一线\"的故事，讲清楚 O 的写法精髓。\n\n**要点速览：**\n- O 是定性的方向，G 是定量的刻度\n- 三个原则：一句话能说清、具象化描述、对齐公司战略\n- 三种错误写法：写成数字、写成废话、写太多\n\n📄 点击查看全文：\nhttps://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd\n\n---\n\n@伟哥 @碧容 @KK @刘军 请大家看看，有建议随时反馈~","targets":["ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209","ou_fd220137ca3825fea85c1a7ef411c261","ou_f396ae36f9888e511a65a32128f422ad","ou_xxx"]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":48534,"output":300,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65218,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368546494}}
