{"type":"message","id":"96881073","parentId":"6d154246","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:38:06.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ace3573af844e97951f2e86","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"📝 第二篇写好了：\n\n**《一季度快结束了，你的OGSM还在执行吗？》**\n\n要点：\n- 三个问题自查：G完成进度、S执行到位吗、有新变化吗\n- KISS 模型复盘\n- 三种情况该调整 OGSM\n- 复盘会三个建议\n\nhttps://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c","target":"user:ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1758,"output":146,"cacheRead":75072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368677103}}
