{"type":"message","id":"3722cfb9","parentId":"a3219c3b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:38:24.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"第二篇写好了，链接：**https://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c**\n\n这篇讲一季度复盘，核心内容：\n- 三个自查问题\n- KISS 模型（Keep/Improve/Start/Stop）\n- 什么时候该调整 OGSM\n- 复盘会怎么开\n\n你看看有什么要改的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":13810,"output":91,"cacheRead":63296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77197,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772368687044}}
