{"type":"message","id":"0d839682","parentId":"6ed37ea8","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:38:34.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，让我查一下碧容、KK、刘军的邮箱："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_731205415c814f9b9f8a7200","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/liuwei/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":230,"output":36,"cacheRead":77056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368705304}}
{"type":"message","id":"5aa15483","parentId":"0d839682","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:38:34.180Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_731205415c814f9b9f8a7200","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 常用联系人\n\n## 高维同事\n- **军哥**（刘军）：lj@gaowei.com\n- **KK**（林传科）：kk@gaowei.com  \n- **碧容**（陈碧容）：cbr@gaowei.com\n\n## 邮箱配置\n- **邮箱地址:** liuwei@gaowei.com\n- **SMTP服务器:** smtp.feishu.cn (SSL, 端口465)\n- **IMAP服务器:** imap.feishu.cn (SSL, 端口993)\n- **密码:** 已配置（不明文存储）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772368714177}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c35b69d","parentId":"5aa15483","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:38:56.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到邮箱了。让我用邮件发送文章："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1331cce5dc7a451e9d8dc1ed","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/ogsm_email.eml << 'EOF'\nFrom: liuwei@gaowei.com\nTo: cbr@gaowei.com, kk@gaowei.com, lj@gaowei.com\nSubject: 两篇OGSM公众号文章初稿，请大家看看\nMIME-Version: 1.0\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8\n\n<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n\n<p>碧容、KK、军哥，好！</p>\n\n<p>伟哥让我写了两篇关于 OGSM 的公众号文章初稿，请大家看看有什么建议。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 8px;\">文章一：OGSM 里 O 怎么写？</h2>\n\n<p>链接：<a href=\"https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd\">https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>核心观点：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>用\"团结群众\"→\"不拿老百姓一针一线\"的故事，讲 O 要从抽象到具体</li>\n<li>三个原则：一句话能说清、具象化描述、对齐公司战略</li>\n<li>三种错误写法：写成数字、写成废话、写太多</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #28a745; padding-bottom: 8px;\">文章二：一季度快结束了，你的 OGSM 还在执行吗？</h2>\n\n<p>链接：<a href=\"https://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c\">https://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>核心观点：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>三个问题自查：G 完成进度、S 执行到位吗、有新变化吗</li>\n<li>KISS 模型复盘：Keep/Improve/Start/Stop</li>\n<li>三种情况该调整 OGSM</li>\n<li>复盘会三个建议</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>两篇文章都来自高维《OGSM业务规划与执行》课程内容，袁园老师主讲。</p>\n\n<p>有什么建议随时反馈~</p>\n\n<p>小龙虾 🦞</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>\nEOF\necho \"Email draft created\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":12565,"output":635,"cacheRead":64896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368714180}}
