{"type":"message","id":"c2e2260d","parentId":"ae3d57be","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:42:27.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c565fe771e8d430cb3a3cb97","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYTHON_SCRIPT'\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.multipart import MIMEMultipart\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nsmtp_server = \"smtp.feishu.cn\"\nsmtp_port = 465\nsender = \"liuwei@gaowei.com\"\npassword = \"AQg6ve0Xpdb3FG87\"\n\nrecipients = [\"lw@gaowei.com\"]\n\nmsg = MIMEMultipart('alternative')\nmsg['From'] = sender\nmsg['To'] = \", \".join(recipients)\nmsg['Subject'] = \"两篇OGSM公众号文章初稿，请大家看看\"\n\nhtml_content = \"\"\"\n<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;\">\n\n<p>碧容、KK、军哥，好！</p>\n\n<p>伟哥让我写了两篇关于 OGSM 的公众号文章初稿，请大家看看有什么建议。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 8px;\">文章一：OGSM 里 O 怎么写？</h2>\n\n<p>链接：<a href=\"https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd\">https://feishu.cn/docx/W8p7dWXZpoXv6Px2zxrcId0ynPd</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>核心观点：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>用\"团结群众\"→\"不拿老百姓一针一线\"的故事，讲 O 要从抽象到具体</li>\n<li>三个原则：一句话能说清、具象化描述、对齐公司战略</li>\n<li>三种错误写法：写成数字、写成废话、写太多</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #28a745; padding-bottom: 8px;\">文章二：一季度快结束了，你的 OGSM 还在执行吗？</h2>\n\n<p>链接：<a href=\"https://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c\">https://feishu.cn/docx/JAwbdtGt2oSqLsxPepFc2kFXn2c</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>核心观点：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>三个问题自查：G 完成进度、S 执行到位吗、有新变化吗</li>\n<li>KISS 模型复盘：Keep/Improve/Start/Stop</li>\n<li>三种情况该调整 OGSM</li>\n<li>复盘会三个建议</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>两篇文章都来自高维《OGSM业务规划与执行》课程内容，袁园老师主讲。</p>\n\n<p>有什么建议随时反馈~</p>\n\n<p>小龙虾 🦞</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\"\"\"\n\nmsg.attach(MIMEText(html_content, 'html', 'utf-8'))\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP_SSL(smtp_server, smtp_port)\n    server.login(sender, password)\n    server.sendmail(sender, recipients, msg.as_string())\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"✅ 已发送到 lw@gaowei.com\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ 发送失败: {e}\")\nPYTHON_SCRIPT"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":250,"output":766,"cacheRead":80704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368923427}}
