{"type":"message","id":"17a51287","parentId":"d439ec63","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:43:27.969Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"邮件回复我看不到，因为邮件是独立系统，不会同步到我这。\n\n两个选择：\n1. **他们回复后，你转发给我** —— 最简单\n2. **他们直接在飞书找我** —— 我能看到飞书消息\n\n或者你让他们直接在飞书私聊我，那样我能实时看到反馈。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":980,"output":69,"cacheRead":80896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772369001364}}
