{"type":"message","id":"4cbaa141","parentId":"fd5b46c8","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:45:10.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以。不过先确认一下：\n\n1. **主题范围**：还是围绕 OGSM，还是扩展到其他高维课程内容（比如 OKR、科学创业、产品创新等）？\n\n2. **文章用途**：公众号发布，还是内部学习资料？\n\n3. **时间安排**：从现在开始每小时一篇？那今晚能写 2-3 篇，明天继续？\n\n你先告诉我方向，我这就开始写第三篇。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":4639,"output":96,"cacheRead":77440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772369104329}}
