{"type":"message","id":"b76a1ff0","parentId":"f2940c13","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:47:10.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e4bc23f250a24369b5ed696a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"gemini \"你是一个专业的公众号文章写手。请帮我把以下内容改写成一篇更生动、更有感染力的公众号文章，要求：\n1. 保留核心观点和案例\n2. 语言更口语化、有节奏感\n3. 适当加入金句和互动问题\n4. 标题要吸引人\n5. 字数控制在1200-1500字\n\n原文主题：目标定得高，为什么总完不成？\n\n核心观点：\n1. 很多公司目标定得高，但策略还是老一套——拿着旧地图找不到新大陆\n2. 目标不变，变的是方法。不是降低目标，而是换打法\n3. 用数学公式拆解目标：销售额 = 流量 × 转化率 × 客单价\n4. 每个变量都要有对应的策略抓手\n5. 案例：保险销售员想年赚100万，按原方法每天要谈16小时不可能，但提高转化率或客单价就能做到\n\n请直接输出改写后的文章，用Markdown格式。\" 2>&1 | head -200","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":504,"output":244,"cacheRead":82368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772369220239}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f1875cd","parentId":"b76a1ff0","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:47:20.702Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e4bc23f250a24369b5ed696a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Options:\n  -m, --model                    Model      [string] [default: \"gemini-2.5-pro\"]\n  -p, --prompt                   Prompt. Appended to input on stdin (if any).\n                                                                        [string]\n  -s, --sandbox                  Run in sandbox?                       [boolean]\n      --sandbox-image            Sandbox image URI.                     [string]\n  -d, --debug                    Run in debug mode?   [boolean] [default: false]\n  -a, --all_files                Include ALL files in context?\n                                                      [boolean] [default: false]\n      --show_memory_usage        Show memory usage in status bar\n                                                      [boolean] [default: false]\n  -y, --yolo                     Automatically accept all actions (aka YOLO\n                                 mode, see\n                                 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xvFZjo5PgG0 for\n                                 more details)?       [boolean] [default: false]\n      --telemetry                Enable telemetry? This flag specifically\n                                 controls if telemetry is sent. Other\n                                 --telemetry-* flags set specific values but do\n                                 not enable telemetry on their own.    [boolean]\n      --telemetry-target         Set the telemetry target (local or gcp).\n                                 Overrides settings files.\n                                              [string] [choices: \"local\", \"gcp\"]\n      --telemetry-otlp-endpoint  Set the OTLP endpoint for telemetry. Overrides\n                                 environment variables and settings files.\n                                                                        [string]\n      --telemetry-log-prompts    Enable or disable logging of user prompts for\n                                 telemetry. Overrides settings files.  [boolean]\n  -c, --checkpointing            Enables checkpointing of file edits\n                                                      [boolean] [default: false]\n  -v, --version                  Show version number                   [boolean]\n  -h, --help                     Show help                             [boolean]\n\nUnknown argument: 你是一个专业的公众号文章写手。请帮我把以下内容改写成一篇更生动、更有感染力的公众号文章，要求：\n1. 保留核心观点和案例\n2. 语言更口语化、有节奏感\n3. 适当加入金句和互动问题\n4. 标题要吸引人\n5. 字数控制在1200-1500字\n\n原文主题：目标定得高，为什么总完不成？\n\n核心观点：\n1. 很多公司目标定得高，但策略还是老一套——拿着旧地图找不到新大陆\n2. 目标不变，变的是方法。不是降低目标，而是换打法\n3. 用数学公式拆解目标：销售额 = 流量 × 转化率 × 客单价\n4. 每个变量都要有对应的策略抓手\n5. 案例：保险销售员想年赚100万，按原方法每天要谈16小时不可能，但提高转化率或客单价就能做到\n\n请直接输出改写后的文章，用Markdown格式。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9669,"aggregated":"Options:\n  -m, --model                    Model      [string] [default: \"gemini-2.5-pro\"]\n  -p, --prompt                   Prompt. Appended to input on stdin (if any).\n                                                                        [string]\n  -s, --sandbox                  Run in sandbox?                       [boolean]\n      --sandbox-image            Sandbox image URI.                     [string]\n  -d, --debug                    Run in debug mode?   [boolean] [default: false]\n  -a, --all_files                Include ALL files in context?\n                                                      [boolean] [default: false]\n      --show_memory_usage        Show memory usage in status bar\n                                                      [boolean] [default: false]\n  -y, --yolo                     Automatically accept all actions (aka YOLO\n                                 mode, see\n                                 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xvFZjo5PgG0 for