{"type":"message","id":"a6b752e4","parentId":"651d0b63","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:51:20.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"第三篇写好了！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_df027e1408f646e3ba07f01e","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"📝 第三篇写好了：\n\n**《目标定得高，为什么总完不成？》**\n\n核心观点：\n- 保险销售员年赚100万的故事——目标没问题，方法有问题\n- 拿着旧地图找不到新大陆\n- 把目标拆成数学公式：流量×转化率×客单价\n- 每个变量都要有策略抓手\n\nhttps://feishu.cn/docx/FbjqdFqgPoCLnMxa5uAcFjZInmJ\n\n---\n\n⏰ 下一篇预计 21:45 开始写","target":"user:ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1621,"output":176,"cacheRead":86080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772369471070}}
