{"type":"message","id":"fa1170ff","parentId":"7c4b9655","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:59:12.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我是 **Claude Opus 4.5**，Anthropic 出品的。\n\n刚才帮你写文章的时候，系统从默认的 GLM-5 切换到了 Opus 4.5。\n\n在 Claude 家族里，Opus 是最强的版本，比 Sonnet 和 Haiku 都强。推理、写作、代码都比较拿手。\n\n---\n\n**当前配置：**\n- 模型：anthropic/claude-opus-4-5\n- Think：off（推理模式关闭）\n- 你的默认模型：zai/glm-5\n\n要不要我继续写第四篇？现在用的是 Opus，质量会比前三篇更好。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":139895,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772369943636}}
