{"type":"message","id":"402ba296","parentId":"fb9ddb77","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:00:36.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01M54RNpLXEf2iUdknw9Cjyk","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"📝 第四篇完成！\n\n**《为什么你的复盘总是走过场》**\n\n核心观点：\n- 复盘就两件事：做得好的保持，做得不好的改进\n- KISS 模型：Keep/Improve/Start/Stop\n- 200个主意法：让团队集体贡献想法\n- 复盘会三个常见错误\n- 金句：踩坑学费不白交，成功经验要沉淀\n\nhttps://feishu.cn/docx/TT2qdUywAo1KrCxClA0ckF6qnxg\n\n---\n\n今天进度：\n✅ 第一篇：OGSM里O怎么写\n✅ 第二篇：一季度快结束了\n✅ 第三篇：目标定得高为什么完不成\n✅ 第四篇：为什么复盘总是走过场\n\n还要继续写吗？现在是21:03","target":"user:ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":150075,"output":394,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150469,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772370028860}}
