{"type":"message","id":"8ce57c6b","parentId":"00e70f65","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:00:42.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **第四篇完成！**\n\n**《为什么你的复盘总是走过场》**\n链接：https://feishu.cn/docx/TT2qdUywAo1KrCxClA0ckF6qnxg\n\n---\n\n**今天进度（4篇）：**\n1. ✅ OGSM 里 O 怎么写\n2. ✅ 一季度快结束了，你的 OGSM 还在执行吗\n3. ✅ 目标定得高，为什么总完不成\n4. ✅ 为什么你的复盘总是走过场\n\n现在是 21:03，还要继续写吗？下一篇我想写**项目管理**或者**跨部门协作**，你看哪个更好？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":150606,"output":229,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772370037352}}
