{"type":"message","id":"17bcf3a2","parentId":"66c9e837","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:09:06.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我需要点击\"发布图文笔记\"。但小红书图文必须有图片，我先生成一张封面图，然后发布："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Xq3gexd5un4giAgUzQ2GmF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' > /tmp/create_cover.html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\nbody { margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n.cover {\n  width: 1080px;\n  height: 1440px;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B6B 0%, #FF8E53 100%);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n  color: white;\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 60px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n.emoji { font-size: 120px; margin-bottom: 40px; }\n.title { font-size: 88px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 30px; }\n.subtitle { font-size: 56px; opacity: 0.9; }\n.tag { \n  margin-top: 60px; \n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); \n  padding: 20px 40px; \n  border-radius: 50px;\n  font-size: 36px;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"cover\">\n  <div class=\"emoji\">❌</div>\n  <div class=\"title\">OGSM的O怎么写？<br>90%的人第一步就错了</div>\n  <div class=\"subtitle\">3个避坑指南 + 正确写法</div>\n  <div class=\"tag\">#职场干货 #目标管理</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\nEOF\necho \"HTML created\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":62669,"output":556,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772370537209}}
