{"type":"message","id":"c5ece655","parentId":"2ef82d7f","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:20:48.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个方式太慢了。让我直接从草稿箱恢复一个或者换个更简单的方案：\n\n**伟哥，小红书的编辑器有点怪，我填的内容总是跑到标题框。**\n\n两个选择：\n1. **我把内容准备好**，你自己复制粘贴发布（最快）\n2. **我继续调试**，可能还要几分钟\n\n你选哪个？内容我已经改好了小红书风格：\n\n---\n\n**标题：** OGSM的O怎么写\n\n**正文：**\n```\n90%的人第一步就错了🤔\n\n先讲个故事👇\n1927年红军战略方向是\"团结群众\"\n结果小战士天天偷老百姓红薯😅\n\n后来改成：「不拿老百姓一针一线」\n执行偏差立刻消失✨\n\n———\n\nO的3个避坑指南：\n❌ 别写数字：这是G不是O\n❌ 别写空话：说了等于没说\n❌ 别写太多：O最多1-2个\n\n正确写法：\n✅ 一句话说清楚\n✅ 具体到能指导行动\n✅ 基层员工能复述\n\nO写歪了，G、S、M全歪💥\n\n#OGSM #目标管理 #职场干货\n```\n\n---\n\n要我继续调试还是你来粘贴？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":118861,"output":423,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772371226882}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2272fee","parentId":"c5ece655","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:20:51.190Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-01 21:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5577eb3d5d34b35c7b620e444b8]\n刘伟: 2\n\n---\nQueued #2\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-01 21:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5577fc70fca4b2cf60645ffebc1]\n刘伟: 怎么样嘞\n\n---\nQueued #3\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-01 21:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b557786e924a0b2de2acc9446cd8]\n刘伟: 你一边发小红书，我们一边聊聊别的可以吗？"}],"timestamp":1772371251181}}
